---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Research & Advisory — Autonomy Bridge"
  description="Decision-grade AI and robotics market research: market sizing, pricing architecture, ICP definition, GTM strategy, and commercial due diligence for automation."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="container site-main">
    <h1>Research &amp; Advisory</h1>
    <p class="subhead reading-column">Decision-Grade AI and Robotics Market Research</p>

    <section class="section reading-column">
      <p>
        Autonomy Bridge produces structured, evidence-forward research for AI, robotics, and
        industrial automation companies evaluating:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Market entry</li>
        <li>Pricing architecture</li>
        <li>Vertical expansion</li>
        <li>Enterprise GTM redesign</li>
        <li>Commercial due diligence</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This page defines capabilities and outputs only.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section reading-column section-alt">
      <h2>Commercialization Research</h2>
      <p>
        Commercialization Research tests whether technical capability translates into durable revenue.
      </p>
      <p>It measures:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deployable SOM after integration and governance filters</li>
        <li>Buyer willingness to pay under budget constraints</li>
        <li>Adoption friction across enterprise systems</li>
        <li>Pilot-to-production conversion thresholds</li>
        <li>Unit economics sensitivity</li>
      </ul>
      <p>This is AI and robotics market research anchored in economic viability.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section reading-column">
      <h2>Research Products</h2>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>Market Opportunity &amp; Sizing Models</h3>
        <p>Bottom-up TAM → SAM → SOM modeling with explicit deployability filters.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>Competitive &amp; Ecosystem Mapping</h3>
        <p>Substitutes, incumbents, integrators, and channel control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>ICP Definition &amp; Segmentation</h3>
        <p>Deployability conditions, not personas.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>Pricing &amp; Packaging Analysis</h3>
        <p>Value metric alignment with budget ownership and accounting treatment.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>Feasibility &amp; Risk Assessment</h3>
        <p>Integration burden, governance veto points, certification friction.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="research-product">
        <h3>GTM &amp; Commercialization Decision Briefs</h3>
        <p>Board-level synthesis with trade-offs and recommendation thresholds.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section reading-column section-alt">
      <h2>Advisory Support</h2>
      <p>Time-bound executive advisory connected to research findings.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>CEO-facing synthesis</li>
        <li>Board-level commercialization risk review</li>
        <li>Non-executional</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section reading-column">
      <h2>What Clients Receive</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Structured deck</li>
        <li>Explicit economic models</li>
        <li>Assumption documentation</li>
        <li>Trade-off analysis</li>
        <li>Clear Go / No-Go recommendation</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section reading-column section-alt">
      <h2>What Autonomy Bridge Does Not Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Implementation or integration</li>
        <li>Marketing operations</li>
        <li>Staff augmentation</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
